text: Khali () is a village located in Bheri municipality in Jajarkot District of Karnali Province of Nepal. The aerial distance from Khali to Nepal's capital Kathmandu is approximately 323 km. ==See also== * Bheri, Jajarkot ==References== Category:Villages in Jajarkot District Category:Populated places in Jajarkot District
title: Khali, Jajarkot
